        "RIGHTWISE": "Righteous. [Obs.] Wyclif.",
        "RIGHTWISELY": "Righteously. [Obs.]",
        "RIGHTWISENESS": "Righteousness. [Obs.]In doom and eke in rightwisnesse. Chaucer.",
