        "ROSY": "Resembling a rose in color, form, or qualities; blooming; red;blushing; also, adorned with roses.A smile that glowed Celestial rosy-red, love's proper hue. Milton.While blooming youth and gay delight Sit thy rosy cheeks confessed.Prior.",
