        "RUDD": "A fresh-water European fish of the Carp family (Leuciscuserythrophthalmus). It is about the size and shape of the roach, butit has the dorsal fin farther back, a stouter body, and red irises.Called also redeye, roud, finscale, and shallow. A blue variety iscalled azurine, or blue roach.",
